{"type": "article", "id": 38504, "title": "LVMH要建电商平台，以及，Rihanna 发布与 Puma第三个联名系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-03-07T03:14:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 4974, "name": "M.A.C"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 27239, "name": "NMD"}, {"id": 38292, "name": "FENTY PUMA"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 632, "name": "巴黎世家"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 17188, "name": "玛丝菲尔"}, {"id": 906, "name": "川久保玲"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 38293, "name": "MIN LIU"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170307105643XRWs2K8lwytveVT6.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/LVMH-prepares-for-launch-of-multi-brand-virtual-department-store,801279.html#.WL33ABJ940o\"><b>奢侈品集团 LVMH 要建大型电商平台</b></a> | 根据 fashionnetwork 报道，LVMH 计划自建一个大型电商平台，除了自有品牌外还会兼售一些设计师品牌，计划于 6 月上线。</p><p><a href=\"http://stock.jrj.com.cn/2017/03/07050122142476.shtml\"><b>深圳女装 Marisfrolg 再次申请 IPO，计划募资 23.8 亿元</b></a> | 时隔三年，深圳玛丝菲尔时装股份有限公司再度申请 IPO。本次玛丝菲尔拟公开发行不超过 5000 万股，计划募资 23.8 亿元。据公开资料显示，玛丝菲尔的主营业务为高端时装的设计、生产及销售，2015 年，公司主力品牌 Marisfrolg 在高端女装市场的综合占有率为 1.31%。</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/balenciaga-names-communication-and-image-director-demna-10837188/\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Balenciaga 任命新的品牌传播形象总监</a><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> | 日前，Balenciaga 任命 Lionel Vermeil 为品牌传播形象总监，任命立即生效。</span></span></span></span></span>上任后，Lionel Vermeil 将负责与 Balenciaga 的创意总监 Demna Gvasalia 一同沟通制定品牌的营销策略和设计品牌形象，并向首席执行官 Cedric Charbit 进行汇报。同时，Lionel Vermeil 还会继续担任开云集团时尚和奢侈情报总监。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/adidas-originals-nmd-cs2-pk-white-core-black\">adidas NMD 家族的人气鞋款 City Sock，曝光最新的 White/Core Black 配色版本</a>。这双鞋依然采用 Primeknit 的袜式鞋身，鞋外侧采用了折叠式的不对称设计，在鞋领处饰以黑色条纹细节，同时搭载 BOOST 中底。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101405aBZm0czWrsGYXnq3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101405UQpruMZEDoLyFinz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>另外，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/06/adidas-nmd-primeknit-backpack/#slide-2\">adidas 还发布了 New NMD Primeknit 背包</a>。把与 NMD 鞋相同的 primeknit 针织技术运用到了背包上，赋予了背包更大的灵活性。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703071014186B3gGEAOTt5zhlSY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101424xz3gmDZTtnPawh6Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703071014247teBAnwqdly9ZJf5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>在 2017 巴黎时装周上，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/comme-des-garcons-x-nike-lunarepic-flyknit-first-look\">川久保玲带来了 Comme des Garçons 与 Nike 的合作鞋款 Nike LunarEpic Flyknit</a>。这双鞋以白色 Flyknit 材质制作的 LunarEpic 为原型，在鞋头位置则加入了黑色蝴蝶结的设计作点缀。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101435fDFU4eQXVi98zbxB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101435BfR2Ij8iUTKelapk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101435XFwUE7L9j80n3PaD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>未来的鞋子会变成什么样子？<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/06/y-3-acronym-sneaker-concept/#slide-5\">Y-3 最近就联手 ACRONYM 发布了一款名叫 Y-A FUYU HIGH 全新概念鞋子</a>。它有着自动鞋带按钮，厚重的、棱角分明的鞋身，看起来极具科幻感。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101445o1TPL4u6mZl8abRY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101445lPAOT70o8t4vCDuc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017030710145925pJsngkEZPMbFTj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101500S248rRVDjgkM7pZn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101506QM6JwxUNO5WjsSoE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.popsugar.com/beauty/MAC-Cosmetics-Min-Liu-Collection-April-2017-43254534?stream_view=1#opening-slide\">M.A.C 与时装设计师 Min Liu 合作推出了一个以传统中国风为主题的 Mythically Charged Collection</a>。全系列以红色、牡丹和金属色调为主，四款不同深浅程度的红色的灵感来自中国山水。这款彩妆将于 4 月 14 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101531pTlu2Uk9tLWVMSIX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307101541r9uHTD1pL0NKdP4t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2017/paris/fenty-puma-by-rihanna/review/\">巴黎时装周上，Rihanna 带来了她的 FENTY PUMA 2017 秋冬系列</a>，这也是她与 PUMA 的第三个合作系列。发布当日，秀场搬到了法国国家图书馆的书库内，模特在书桌上走秀，旁边摆着一列图书馆灯。该系列包括多款毛衣和外套、篮球短裤、运动服、短裤和运动衫，都带着点 Rihanna 那种特有的“坏女孩”感觉。来看看：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104900gZIQXacjbeOxU9vF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104900DY32FBXIziTmhxaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104901HUsMcvAS0dYuybz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104901FTsE1tALJn4lwOr8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104901m8VL0f3ZvlOzn1UC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104901Slkt3GVOU96uiKZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104902moVAeqgsibw32dSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104900N9n56qeW8AQJVLgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104902OZmjQ2D1TWA0gJc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104902Ol6H1DP0MTeiIoud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703071049032veDLJ10WsclE5qG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104902BPqjEsYO053dyF18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104903R8mw6UXKoABSETaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104904BQdfwzXDFsjPKJm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104905ihfLZ02Eud8kUrQg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104905VFsTO8oxtELC2n5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104905Jr0iQ8uqTw3Eo5sV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017030710490634vsNT96MBVgxWRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104906dUqxFsp9TlS6wBcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104907H7hcxvnOZTF2Sj40.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104908A5o1V4Xkyl6bYnxR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104908JA5kow1lypVBhYus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104908Aet2bs1rOuX8Q30w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170307104908saq92T3fZVyO8NSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2017/paris/fenty-puma-by-rihanna/review/\">wwd</a></p>"}